text: The 880s Decade began on 1 January 880 and ended on 31 December 889. It is distinct from the decade known as the 89th decade which began on January 1, 881 and ended on December 31, 890. == Events == * 885: Vikings lay siege to Paris * 886: Alfred the Great of Wessex captures London == Important people == * Charles the Fat * Alfred the Great * Basil I
title: 880s
